msgid ""
"An old Barbarian proverb<br> meaning that you need to take some risks "
"sometimes."
msgstr "Un antic proverbi bàrbar diu que <br>algunes vegades s'han d'assumir riscos."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a building
#: ../../data/tribes/buildings/productionsites/barbarians/ax_workshop/helptexts.lua:13
